content:
Design Your Quick Text Strategy

Before using quick text, run through these planning questions to use it effectively and save time. 

Required Editions:
Available in: Group, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, Developer Editions (Classic)
Available in: Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, Developer Editions (Lightning)

Who should use quick text?
All or most users for customer communications in various channels.

Quick Text Channels:
Email
Event
Internal
Knowledge
Chat
Messaging
Phone
Portal
Social
Task

Who can create and share quick text messages?
Service agents to maintain their own.
Supervisors to share with other users.

Do you need separate quick text sets for business units?
Yes, if multiple units have unique processes, customers, and terminology.

In which scenarios does your team need quick text messages?
Standardize messaging for customer service chat greetings, responses to FAQs, introductions to new products or promotions.

title: Designing a Quick Text Strategy for Service Cloud
